snippet.title: The SoulKeeper VR - E3 2019 Trailer Extended Version
snippet.description:
The SoulKeeper VR extended version of the trailer presented at UploadVR's E3 2019 VR Showcase. Still in development. Target platforms: PC (Oculus Rift, Rift S, Valve Index, HTC Vive/Vive Pro, WMR headsets). 

Subscribe to our mailing list on http://www.thesoulkeeper.com
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/SoulKeeperGame
